    "headline": "Ameriprise Financial Earns Technology Innovation Award for its Ameriprise® Signature Wealth Program",
    "summary": "MINNEAPOLIS, June 11, 2026--Ameriprise Financial (NYSE: AMP) today announced it has received the 2026 Technology Innovation Award from the Bank Insurance & Securities Association (BISA). This award recognizes the Ameriprise® Signature Wealth Program, a flexible unified managed account (UMA) that enables advisors to seamlessly combine multiple investment options and management methods into one portfolio.",
